%description
"Math.NumberTheory.Logarithms" and "Math.NumberTheory.Powers.Integer" from the
arithmoi package.

Also provides "GHC.Integer.Logarithms.Compat" and
"Math.NumberTheory.Power.Natural" modules, as well as some additional functions
in migrated modules.

